{"data": [{"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "0_1707442739.576066", "card_id": "Q_643366218", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 212}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "大数据杀熟疑云，「三台手机同时买票差价三倍」，如何看待此事？是否真的是杀熟？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "日前，有网友发现，在飞猪平台订机票时，发现同一天、同一时间、同一趟航班 (郑州飞珠海)3 个手机显示 3 种价格，并且苹果手机价格最贵，质疑称是大数据杀熟。 视频显示，3 台手机所显示的同一天同一趟航班的价格分别为 400 元、 481 元和 1330 元，显示 1330 元价格的是苹果手机。其中，400 元的价格下方显示「经济舱 2.6 折」，481 元的价格下方显示「优惠前 1330」，1330 元价格的下方显示「经济舱 8.7 折」。 1 月 18 日，飞猪方面回应澎湃新闻称，前一日起正在尝试联系视频中客户核实情况，不排除为代理商价格投放错误或视频中账号领取过大额优惠券，若消费者发现价格异常可第一时间联系飞猪处理。（澎湃新闻）大数据杀熟疑云：3 台手机同时买票差价 3 倍，是不是杀熟？- 中新网"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-45cc4d9f9cfcf53a523bbdfceb0fa444_1440w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "259 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/643366218"}}, "attached_info": "CkAIhYrzh/6JpqBKEAMaCTEwNTI0ODAzMSCmzIuuBjAAOOIFQAByCTY0MzM2NjIxOHgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "1_1707442739.577058", "card_id": "Q_643269258", "card_label": {"type": "hot", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 30}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何评价郑晓龙执导、白敬亭主演的刑侦剧《南来北往》？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-4c66e8f7c0a62de23bc94d4f1e7a98fa_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "111 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/643269258"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8IhYrzh/6JpqBKEAMaCTEwNTIyNjM4NCCsooiuBjAAOC1AAXIJNjQzMjY5MjU4eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", 